message:

the problem is PPBUS_G3H  i have only 3.4v.
PP3V42_G3H is ok 3.5v.

title: [SOLVED]Macbook pro 13 A1278 Dont turn On
message: Resistance over C7050 and C7020??, voltage on pin 2 from ISL??

title: [SOLVED]Macbook pro 13 A1278 Dont turn On
message: C7050 and c7020 = 3.3V BOUGHT side. pin 2 = 16.75v

title: [SOLVED]Macbook pro 13 A1278 Dont turn On
message: Ive said "resistance" over C7020 and C7050 not voltage... resistance between pin 1 and pin 2 of each capacitor...

title: [SOLVED]Macbook pro 13 A1278 Dont turn On
message: Remove F7040 and check if PPBUS_G3H goes high (12.6V), if dont, measure in diode mode pin1 from F7040 and report value, also check that isl is soldered correctly..
